face quantum Hall physics, superconductivity and\nnonequilibrium polariton condensates is likely to provide fertile ground for\ninvestigation of completely new physical phenomena.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2015 16:07:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-02-17"}
