on of the output of low-depth quantum\ncircuits, which may be of independent interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 7 Oct 2015 19:59:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 25 Oct 2015 16:14:52 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 21 Nov 2016 20:10:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-22"}
